                <div class="alert alert-info shadow-sm fw-semibold">After payment, send proof (Screenshot / Reference Number / Transaction ID or Counter Slip) along with your Paper ID.</div>
                <div class="alert alert-warning shadow-sm fw-semibold">At least one author of each accepted paper must register and attend the conference.</div>
                <div class="alert alert-info shadow-sm fw-semibold">Selected paper abstracts will be published in the conference proceedings with ISBN.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

